@startuml state
skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam defaultFontName "Arial"
skinparam defaultFontSize 12
skinparam StateBorderColor #888888
skinparam StateBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam ArrowColor #555555
skinparam NoteBackgroundColor #FFFDE7
skinparam NoteBorderColor #F9A825

title Backgammon - Game Phase State Machine

[*] --> rollingForFirst : App start / new game

state "rollingForFirst\nBoth players roll for first move" as rollingForFirst
state "waitingForRoll\nWaiting for current player to roll" as waitingForRoll
state "playerActing\nPlayer selects checkers and moves" as playerActing
state "playerDecidingDouble\nAccept or decline doubling cube" as playerDecidingDouble
state "aiThinking\nAI evaluates and executes moves" as aiThinking
state "gameOver\nWinner announced" as gameOver

rollingForFirst --> waitingForRoll       : Higher roll wins

waitingForRoll  --> playerActing         : Player rolls dice
waitingForRoll  --> aiThinking           : AI turn (auto-roll)

playerActing    --> playerActing         : Sub-move applied\n(dice remaining)
playerActing    --> playerDecidingDouble : Doubling cube offered
playerActing    --> waitingForRoll       : All dice used\n(AI turn next)
playerActing    --> gameOver             : Last checker borne off

note right of playerActing
  MoveGenerator computes
  legal sequences each sub-move.
  Turn auto-ends when no
  legal moves remain.
end note

playerDecidingDouble --> playerActing : Accept (cube x2)
playerDecidingDouble --> gameOver     : Decline (opponent wins)

aiThinking --> waitingForRoll : AI turn complete
aiThinking --> gameOver       : AI bears off last checker

note right of aiThinking
  BackgammonAI selects
  highest scoring MoveSequence
  via heuristic evaluation.
end note

gameOver --> waitingForRoll : Next game (match continues)
gameOver --> [*]            : Match over

@enduml
